{"tid":1602950,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［戰術]***不說跑呀衝緊埋黎！試說一二一二！***","createTime":"2019-09-29T14:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:39:07.000Z","uid":13586,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e6ec6caadb8e13c81f1f6388ea1885471cce0b0b","tid":1602950,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:35:27.000Z","msg":"三個月喇<br />\n<br />\nHit and run 都講咗兩個月喇，都仲係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>一味叫走走走，見人走我就走</strong></span>，後面半gear同和理非嚇到雞飛狗走都唔知咩事，搞到走散哂，前線好易缺人！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n不說走走走，試說急步行<br />\n不說跑呀衝緊埋黎，試說一二一二<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，三個月資訊都仲停留喺嗰邊有狗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>邊度嗰邊！防暴便衣定速龍！數量！</strong></span><br />\n咁模糊嘅資訊好難叫大家部署，然後又係一味走<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我要時地人一句過！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不說嗰邊有狗，試說鵝頸橋五十防暴<br />\n不說呢邊有狗，試說海富橋四十速龍</strong></span>"},{"pid":"63a1e525e59f803fcdc4140473eacee022be0f4b","tid":1602950,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:36:47.000Z","msg":"戰術post推你老母"},{"pid":"bbe1d2d1b2b699a7a7f1750c0cced981efc5ca68","tid":1602950,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:37:02.000Z","msg":"真心睇唔過眼"},{"pid":"1baa38a7b4468346ee69a2c08d4dcfdee6d9bc5d","tid":1602950,"uid":13586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"灣仔狗屋條橋十零隻，橋底成千手足都唔召喚獅鳥，搞撚錯"},{"pid":"d29f6ed17c03441a8a32e0edd2a9d90aeff466c8","tid":1602950,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">612<br />\n721<br />\n831<br />\n新屋嶺集中營</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e8b85e4379752a67e8f8dc69675c74d0f7c877c5","tid":1602950,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌那媽頂硬上</span>"},{"pid":"1a38a7d3b8f55bc4389d5b2cd1f5657053334a00","tid":1602950,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:40:35.000Z","msg":"仲有呀<br />\n<br />\n唔好再做散水撚留力撚呀<br />\n71又話留力<br />\n85三罷留力<br />\n831又話留力<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十一賀佢老母係咪都係留力呀</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2707ab9b08292f5b8cf37e8d04e2b153558e0a0c","tid":1602950,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:45:46.000Z","msg":"你老母想做發資訊嘅專業啲啦<br />\n<br />\n今日聽咗十鳩廿萬次呢邊有狗嗰邊有狗<br />\n<br />\n我要時地人一句過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">乜撚野叫「走呀！嗰邊有狗！」<br />\n我要「循道衛理一百防暴！」</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"76f129738b172adbe1af8d507595334962fd82da","tid":1602950,"uid":46078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:46:12.000Z","msg":"聽日 930 全港三罷"},{"pid":"59e030bd876ef25b9d803f46e9957a2f24de09d8","tid":1602950,"uid":12197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:46:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9386fd6e8e40fca4847d97bfdb80563232cad2d0","tid":1602950,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:46:50.000Z","msg":"戰術post冇人理"},{"pid":"80bb0f3adba08d590e47cc913fa6f31c510dee05","tid":1602950,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"人手推上熱門"},{"pid":"b4de02b2aa81fdd97a2aafebfcc4cd60c5f546ae","tid":1602950,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"哨兵專業啲唔該！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">不要說「走呀！嗰邊有狗！」<br />\n試說「添華道出水炮車」</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"128a280a1bb14708384a1b9bafc8740293e88b7a","tid":1602950,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"推你老母"},{"pid":"67b67527bb3775c8942199152a1243e90444aad2","tid":1602950,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:57:04.000Z","msg":"我推"},{"pid":"562a3bdcd55323ac6bcd95d8927d818160906d15","tid":1602950,"uid":6882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:59:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"703b5193520678a38b327d190a083959947cd7e8","tid":1602950,"uid":312150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"破你五連"},{"pid":"d523b2ec85e04da24c83e14af6c228a99ae247f0","tid":1602950,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"703b5193520678a38b327d190a083959947cd7e8","tid":1602950,"uid":312150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"破你五連"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:00:08.000Z","msg":"破我多啲"},{"pid":"d1f6db10f31bd07b787ada37b8b9691e1425d9d0","tid":1602950,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>不要說「走呀！狗衝緊埋嚟！」<br />\n試說「急步走！一二一二！」</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5f4b23fbec5df471ec370edaa259822add4ed029","tid":1602950,"uid":312150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d523b2ec85e04da24c83e14af6c228a99ae247f0","tid":1602950,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"703b5193520678a38b327d190a083959947cd7e8","tid":1602950,"uid":312150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"破你五連"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:00: